text: Enviken is a locality situated in Falun Municipality, Dalarna County, Sweden with 609 inhabitants in 2010. Residents of Enviken are known to harbor a nostalgia for mid-20th century Americana complete with a fondness for rockabilly and classic American automobiles.National Geographic, June 2010 at page 16.http://ngm.nationalgeographic.com/visions-of-earth/visions-earth-2010 Enviken is also the name of a record company in the Swedish province of Dalarna. == References == Category:Populated places in Dalarna County Category:Populated places in Falun Municipality
title: Enviken
